11. Eviction API

Never delete Pods directly.

Use

Eviction API

because it

✔ Checks PDB

✔ Gracefully terminates Pods

✔ Respects terminationGracePeriodSeconds

Cluster tools such as kubectl drain use the Eviction API rather than deleting Pods directly.

12. Rolling Updates vs PDB

Many beginners think

Rolling Update
↓

PDB

Wrong.

Deployment rolling updates are governed by the Deployment strategy (maxSurge, maxUnavailable), not blocked by the PDB. PDB mainly protects against voluntary disruptions such as node drains.

