15. New DisruptionTarget Pod Condition

Modern Kubernetes adds

DisruptionTarget

It indicates that a Pod is about to be terminated due to a disruption, with reasons such as:

EvictionByEvictionAPI
PreemptionByScheduler
DeletionByTaintManager
TerminationByKubelet
DeletionByPodGC

This condition helps with observability and advanced workload behavior.

